<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Letter of Intent - {{deal.name}}</title>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="letterhead">
    <div class="company-info">
      <strong>{{deal.buyerName}}</strong><br>
      {{deal.buyerAddress}}<br>
      {{deal.buyerCity}}, {{deal.buyerState}} {{deal.buyerZip}}
    </div>
    <div class="date">{{date generatedAt 'long'}}</div>
  </div>

  <div class="recipient">
    <strong>{{deal.sellerName}}</strong><br>
    {{deal.sellerAddress}}<br>
    {{deal.sellerCity}}, {{deal.sellerState}} {{deal.sellerZip}}
  </div>

  <div class="subject">
    <strong>Re: Letter of Intent - {{deal.name}}</strong><br>
    Property Address: {{deal.propertyAddress}}, {{deal.city}}, {{deal.state}} {{deal.zipCode}}
  </div>

  <div class="body">
    <p>Dear {{deal.sellerContact}}:</p>

    <p>
      This Letter of Intent ("LOI") sets forth the principal terms upon which
      <strong>{{deal.buyerName}}</strong> or its designee ("Buyer") is prepared to acquire the
      real property and improvements commonly known as <strong>{{deal.name}}</strong>, located at
      {{deal.propertyAddress}}, {{deal.city}}, {{deal.state}} {{deal.zipCode}} (the "Property")
      from <strong>{{deal.sellerName}}</strong> ("Seller").
    </p>

    <h3>1. PURCHASE PRICE</h3>
    <p>
      The purchase price for the Property shall be
      <strong>
        {{#provField "purchasePrice" model.purchasePrice}}
          {{currency model.purchasePrice}}
        {{/provField}}
      </strong>
      (the "Purchase Price"), payable in cash at closing, subject to prorations and adjustments.
    </p>

    <h3>2. EARNEST MONEY DEPOSIT</h3>
    <p>
      Within three (3) business days following the mutual execution of the Purchase Agreement,
      Buyer shall deposit <strong>{{currency deal.earnestMoneyDeposit}}</strong> (the "Initial Deposit")
      with the Title Company. An additional deposit of <strong>{{currency deal.additionalDeposit}}</strong>
      shall be due upon expiration of the Due Diligence Period. All deposits shall be credited
      toward the Purchase Price at closing.
    </p>

    <h3>3. DUE DILIGENCE PERIOD</h3>
    <p>
      Buyer shall have <strong>{{deal.dueDiligenceDays}} days</strong> from the Effective Date
      (the "Due Diligence Period") to conduct its due diligence investigation of the Property.
      During this period, Buyer may terminate the Purchase Agreement for any reason or no reason,
      in which case the Initial Deposit shall be refunded to Buyer.
    </p>

    <h3>4. CLOSING</h3>
    <p>
      The closing of the transaction (the "Closing") shall occur within
      <strong>{{deal.closingDays}} days</strong> following the expiration of the Due Diligence Period,
      or such earlier date as mutually agreed upon by the parties.
    </p>

    <h3>5. TITLE AND SURVEY</h3>
    <p>
      Seller shall convey fee simple title to the Property by special warranty deed, subject only
      to the Permitted Exceptions. Buyer shall obtain a current ALTA survey and owner's title
      insurance policy at Buyer's expense.
    </p>

    <h3>6. PROPERTY CONDITION</h3>
    <p>
      The Property shall be conveyed in its "AS-IS, WHERE-IS" condition as of the Effective Date,
      subject to Seller's representations and warranties in the Purchase Agreement. Seller shall
      maintain the Property in its current condition through Closing.
    </p>

    <h3>7. FINANCING</h3>
    <p>
      This transaction {{#if deal.financingContingency}}is{{else}}is not{{/if}} contingent upon
      Buyer obtaining financing. Buyer intends to finance the acquisition with
      {{#provField "loanAmount" model.loanAmount}}
        {{currency model.loanAmount}}
      {{/provField}}
      of senior debt ({{percent metrics.ltv}} LTV).
    </p>

    <h3>8. ACCESS</h3>
    <p>
      Seller shall provide Buyer and its representatives with reasonable access to the Property
      and all books, records, leases, contracts, and other documents relating to the Property
      during the Due Diligence Period.
    </p>

    <h3>9. CONFIDENTIALITY</h3>
    <p>
      Both parties agree to keep the terms of this LOI and all information exchanged during
      negotiations confidential, except as required by law or to their respective advisors
      and lenders who agree to maintain such confidentiality.
    </p>

    <h3>10. EXCLUSIVITY</h3>
    <p>
      During the period commencing on the date this LOI is executed and ending on the earlier of
      (a) <strong>{{deal.exclusivityDays}} days</strong> thereafter, (b) the mutual execution of the
      Purchase Agreement, or (c) the termination of negotiations, Seller agrees not to solicit,
      negotiate, or accept any other offers for the sale of the Property.
    </p>

    <h3>11. NON-BINDING</h3>
    <p>
      <strong>THIS LETTER OF INTENT IS NOT INTENDED TO CREATE, AND SHALL NOT BE CONSTRUED AS
      CREATING, A BINDING AGREEMENT BETWEEN THE PARTIES</strong>, except for the provisions
      regarding Confidentiality and Exclusivity, which shall be binding upon the parties.
      The parties' obligations shall arise only upon the mutual execution of a definitive
      Purchase Agreement.
    </p>

    <h3>12. EXPENSES</h3>
    <p>
      Each party shall bear its own costs and expenses in connection with the negotiation and
      execution of this LOI and the Purchase Agreement.
    </p>

    <h3>13. EXPIRATION</h3>
    <p>
      This LOI shall expire if not executed by both parties by <strong>5:00 PM local time</strong>
      on <strong>{{date deal.loiExpirationDate 'long'}}</strong>.
    </p>

    <p class="closing-paragraph">
      If the foregoing terms are acceptable, please sign below and return one executed copy to
      the undersigned. Upon receipt, we will promptly prepare and circulate a draft Purchase
      Agreement for your review.
    </p>

    <p>Sincerely,</p>
  </div>

  {{!-- Buyer Signature --}}
  <div class="signature-section">
    <div class="signature-block">
      <div class="signature-header">BUYER:</div>
      <div class="signature-company">{{deal.buyerName}}</div>
      <div class="signature-line"></div>
      <div class="signature-name">By: ___________________________</div>
      <div class="signature-title">Name: _________________________</div>
      <div class="signature-title">Title: _________________________</div>
      <div class="signature-title">Date: _________________________</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  {{!-- Seller Signature --}}
  <div class="signature-section acceptance">
    <div class="acceptance-header">ACCEPTED AND AGREED:</div>
    <div class="signature-block">
      <div class="signature-header">SELLER:</div>
      <div class="signature-company">{{deal.sellerName}}</div>
      <div class="signature-line"></div>
      <div class="signature-name">By: ___________________________</div>
      <div class="signature-title">Name: _________________________</div>
      <div class="signature-title">Title: _________________________</div>
      <div class="signature-title">Date: _________________________</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  {{!-- Key Terms Summary (for internal reference) --}}
  <div class="page-break"></div>
  <div class="internal-summary">
    <h3>KEY TERMS SUMMARY (Internal Reference Only)</h3>
    <table>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>Purchase Price</strong></td>
        <td>{{currency model.purchasePrice}}</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>Price/Unit</strong></td>
        <td>{{currency metrics.pricePerUnit}}</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>Going-In Cap Rate</strong></td>
        <td>{{percent metrics.goingInCapRate}}</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>NOI</strong></td>
        <td>{{currency model.noi}}</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>Proposed Loan</strong></td>
        <td>{{currency model.loanAmount}} ({{percent metrics.ltv}} LTV)</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>Equity Required</strong></td>
        <td>{{currency metrics.equityRequired}}</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>Initial Deposit</strong></td>
        <td>{{currency deal.earnestMoneyDeposit}}</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>DD Period</strong></td>
        <td>{{deal.dueDiligenceDays}} days</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>Closing Timeline</strong></td>
        <td>{{deal.closingDays}} days post-DD</td>
      </tr>
    </table>

    <h4>Data Sources</h4>
    <ul>
      {{#each inputs}}
        <li><strong>{{@key}}</strong>: {{this.documentName}} {{#if this.documentCell}}({{this.documentCell}}){{/if}}</li>
      {{/each}}
    </ul>
  </div>
</body>
</html>

<style>
  body {
    max-width: 7in;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .letterhead {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-bottom: 2em;
    padding-bottom: 1em;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #0A0A0A;
  }

  .company-info {
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .date {
    text-align: right;
  }

  .recipient {
    margin-bottom: 1.5em;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .subject {
    margin-bottom: 2em;
    padding: 12px;
    background: #F5F5F5;
    border-left: 4px solid #0A0A0A;
  }

  .body h3 {
    margin-top: 1.5em;
    margin-bottom: 0.5em;
    font-size: 11pt;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }

  .body p {
    text-align: justify;
  }

  .closing-paragraph {
    margin-top: 2em;
  }

  .signature-section {
    margin-top: 2em;
    page-break-inside: avoid;
  }

  .signature-block {
    width: 300px;
  }

  .signature-header {
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.5em;
  }

  .signature-company {
    margin-bottom: 0.5em;
  }

  .signature-line {
    border-top: 1px solid #171717;
    margin-top: 50px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .signature-name,
  .signature-title {
    margin-top: 4px;
    font-size: 10pt;
  }

  .acceptance {
    margin-top: 3em;
    padding-top: 2em;
    border-top: 1px dashed #A3A3A3;
  }

  .acceptance-header {
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 12pt;
    margin-bottom: 1em;
  }

  .internal-summary {
    background: #FFFBEB;
    border: 2px dashed #F59E0B;
    padding: 20px;
    margin-top: 2em;
  }

  .internal-summary h3 {
    color: #B45309;
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .internal-summary table {
    width: 100%;
    margin: 1em 0;
  }

  .internal-summary td {
    padding: 6px 12px;
    border: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #FDE68A;
  }

  .internal-summary ul {
    font-size: 9pt;
    color: #737373;
  }
</style>
